data.title: Adventure Time
data.description:
Something completely different for a change! This piece was done for a charity auction, it will be printed on a quality paper, framed and auctioned! The money will help kids with disabilities get access to quality equipment in their education process.  I was really honored to contribute to this beautiful event hosted by the amazing people at Polska Grafika Cyfrowa (http://polskagrafikacyfrowa.pl/)!

Big thanks to my bro in arts Mathias Zamecki helping my stubborn mind understand stylized imagery a little better.

data.title: "RISE" - Proof of concept
data.description:
www.conceptrise.com

Proof of concept for RISE, where I had an opportunity to do some great stuff. If the winds will be good, then It will be made as full feature film, so keep Your fingers crossed and eyes open.

I was responsible for the opening shots / look development / shading / lighting and rendering. Ive had some input in other shots with partial modeling and...bla bla bla.... all that stuff.

It was a huge pleasure to work with one of the best Director I know David Karlak. And I was put next to such a crazy talents like Scott Metzger, Danny Yount, Greg Broadmore, Mike Hill, Chris Brown, Daniel Dany Nisz, Arkadiusz Leszko, and way way more. I bow to the Director and the whole Team. WONDERFULL work everyone!!!

data.title: Katana - Low Poly
data.description:
Low poly katana I created by reworking an old high poly model. 
My own design, therefore not 100% authentic but believable.
